    Class
    Description
    Book
    Represents a Book with various attributes such as id, title, author, description, genre, and a cover image URL.
    BookInfo
    Represents information about a book, including its status and associated book details.
    DBComands
    The DBComands class provides a collection of methods for interacting with a database.
    ImReading
    The ImReading class is responsible for managing and displaying a list of books currently associated with a user.
    MyReads
    The MyReads class represents a user's collection of books in a reading list.
    myReadsScroll
    The myReadsScroll class is a custom JavaFX ScrollPane designed to display a grid of book covers with interactive functionality for selection and actions such as deletion or click-handling.
    PaneCarte
    PaneCarte is a custom UI component that displays information about a book in a visually structured horizontal layout.
    Review
    Represents a review entry associated with a user and a book.
    ReviewScroll
    The ReviewScroll class is a custom extension of the ScrollPane that acts as a container for displaying user reviews associated with a specific book.
    ScrollPanel
    Represents a custom scrollable panel designed for displaying a grid of book covers.
    SearchResultsScroll
    Represents a custom scroll pane for displaying a list of books as a scrollable grid.
    Star
    Represents a visual star UI component that extends the Button class.
